亿美元的黄金。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/1h75OAigbf2mhpl9mNat2AeC_hu-eqyBZUS0_TbPR6Ml7mLV4IkV_SOp67o4ZZaPU7DzuVgVehPbQ5pjK2CGsVpCFf9qyj8KhHUIHZa7Pmig-cuTjMvpDSNR6AyyMdWW5qJW4z2MvMWhozuMwfSmeHNgRqLetDQL4vmueOgVnMLN7Y1UNG-gUmD91klHuufZT8p_dhjBicy_vnVnbJ38zqPh_a875W-ee7zIdB0FkO-cRhZ8FT2fmU_-5FRoLOiVRjXXKXNzS0vtbunuIDBZWQPGjg/LUfL5TYS63_liIeLaO8mr-H8fvZ0lxCz/9" target="_blank"&gt;避风港资产的积累&lt;/a&gt;凸显了一些国家对美元过度暴露的人们日益关注的问题。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/J_YZs3t9jJYcNVe2tvRneQJQEs1XVKCA4cV9zUmvElKUDBoPAw6UGwmWwN0UvO8njxrUwzeEzK7cqoLL_ggbM4HK0ADYq-_PVcufqS2BxxlYbppHSc-ZFYUAftOdSN5R4olpFT8pDXlh1F7qqs6Hk4e3qIwkNdVqROqUuBsrDY8Vq8rPUF3G21n6oWZPAgWJ38fVA5e3RmDWsf1zrjnygsdoYHzX4EwjsTmtFyWWNbSC5WaCIhKrdDKixZ_Y9UolJSu7az5OwlsLbHXeC13ERJV_HQ/4syuW6f8D61kdoBfINny7bOXp-PXTMVo/9" target="_blank"&gt;黄金价格的集会&lt;/a&gt;只会增加金属的吸引力。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;大部分购买都是秘密的，&lt;/strong&gt;但贸易数据表明，中国以及其他未知的买家通过瑞士占了很多购买。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Jre1sXtTyd-a04EB7KDPXxY44bDJIH047IKHojc7kwAi12XwssqipByznLDqLCHKQykt5n1TDJ5LeIPTMmnMu9k_DKz8yf6CF3qCMnBVCaJoPqQYuCquPx3kjYIPsoZRDCXB_-f5sk-SAuobhrp33slOdTFvI1jz6HX0Qtf6O48kVj8IGqs27nK__PPqgcBTzr4Ttml_-ej0bloDG0CrG6Ule6EUWqx7lWS2Je1Ml1WmfnZkZtZ_TChFrU94WPJ2G6hz01L-fVzax3UFGrSHzMsV0Q/hAcj71vsc3WwL6b0f9hydK1ehg5HAVp6/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ibra.gh_eRnw/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="alt" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ibra.gh_eRnw/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; m